---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base
  title="About Hexagamers"
  description="Learn about Hexagamers — a board game review and guide site for tabletop enthusiasts of all experience levels."
>
  <div class="about-page">
    <div class="container">
      <header class="about-header fade-up">
        <p class="section-label">About</p>
        <h1>Built by a Board Gamer,<br/>For Board Gamers</h1>
      </header>

      <div class="about-body">
        <div class="about-content fade-up fade-up-1">
          <p class="lead">
            Hexagamers is a board game blog dedicated to helping you find your next great game — whether you're a seasoned strategist or someone who just opened their first box of Catan.
          </p>
          <p>
            Every review, how-to-play guide, and best-of list on this site comes from real playthroughs and genuine enthusiasm for tabletop gaming. No paid promotions, no fluff — just honest opinions on games we've actually played.
          </p>
          <h2>What You'll Find Here</h2>
          <ul class="feature-list">
            <li>
              <span class="feature-icon" aria-hidden="true">★</span>
              <div>
                <strong>Reviews</strong> — Detailed takes on what works, what doesn't, who'll love it, and whether it's worth the price.
              </div>
            </li>
            <li>
              <span class="feature-icon" aria-hidden="true">◎</span>
              <div>
                <strong>How-To-Play Guides</strong> — Simplified rulebooks so your group spends less time reading and more time playing.
              </div>
            </li>
            <li>
              <span class="feature-icon" aria-hidden="true">◈</span>
              <div>
                <strong>Best-Of Lists</strong> — Curated picks by player count, age, category, and occasion.
              </div>
            </li>
          </ul>
          <h2>Affiliate Disclosure</h2>
          <p>
            Some links on this site are Amazon affiliate links. If you buy a game through one of those links, we earn a small commission at no extra cost to you. It helps keep the site running. We only recommend games we genuinely like.
          </p>
        </div>

        <aside class="about-sidebar fade-up fade-up-2">
          <div class="sidebar-card">
            <div class="hex-badge" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 80 92" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                <path d="M40 2L78 23V69L40 90L2 69V23L40 2Z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
                <path d="M40 16L66 31V61L40 76L14 61V31L40 16Z" fill="currentColor" fill-opacity="0.08" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"/>
                <text x="40" y="56" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Georgia,serif" font-weight="900" font-size="28" fill="currentColor">H</text>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <p class="sidebar-tagline">Board games for every table.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="sidebar-stats">
            <div class="about-stat">
              <span class="about-stat-num">100+</span>
              <span class="about-stat-label">Games Reviewed</span>
            </div>
            <div class="about-stat">
              <span class="about-stat-num">4</span>
              <span class="about-stat-label">Content Types</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </aside>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Base>

<style>
.about-page { padding: 4rem 0 6rem; }
.about-header { margin-bottom: 3.5rem; }
.about-header h1 { margin-top: 0.5rem; }

.about-body {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 320px;
  gap: 4rem;
  align-items: start;
}

.about-content .lead {
  font-size: 1.15rem;
  color: var(--text-2);
  line-height: 1.75;
  margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
}
.about-content p { margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: var(--text-2); }
.about-content h2 {
  margin-top: 2.5rem;
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
  font-size: 1.4rem;
}

.feature-list {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 1.25rem;
  margin-bottom: 2rem;
}
.feature-list li {
  display: flex;
  gap: 1rem;
  align-items: flex-start;
}
.feature-icon {
  color: var(--amber);
  font-size: 1.1rem;
  flex-shrink: 0;
  margin-top: 0.1em;
  line-height: 1.5;
}
.feature-list strong { color: var(--text); }

.about-sidebar { position: sticky; top: 6rem; }
.sidebar-card {
  background: var(--surface);
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
  padding: 2rem;
  text-align: center;
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
}
.hex-badge {
  width: 80px;
  height: 92px;
  color: var(--amber);
  margin: 0 auto 1rem;
}
.hex-badge svg { width: 100%; height: 100%; }
.sidebar-tagline {
  font-family: var(--font-display);
  font-style: italic;
  color: var(--text-2);
  font-size: 1rem;
}
.sidebar-stats {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 1rem;
}
.about-stat {
  background: var(--surface);
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
  padding: 1.25rem;
  text-align: center;
}
.about-stat-num {
  display: block;
  font-family: var(--font-display);
  font-size: 2rem;
  font-weight: 900;
  color: var(--amber);
  line-height: 1;
}
.about-stat-label {
  display: block;
  font-size: 0.7rem;
  letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--text-3);
  margin-top: 0.3rem;
}

@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .about-body { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .about-sidebar { position: static; }
}
</style>
